{"tid":785583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每次搭車經過墳場 都覺得好壓抑","createTime":"2018-08-19T10:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T14:46:35.000Z","uid":182701,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72620ebbc75910581eda63c9ed577dd020522a3e","tid":785583,"uid":182701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:27:13.000Z","msg":"究竟每日咁辛苦做人係為左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前細個好怕死<br />\n覺得死左咩都做唔到 <br />\n連思想都冇埋 世界發生d咩<br />\n我唔會知 亦都唔關我事<br />\n<br />\n連訓教都唔想<br />\n覺得訓教好晒時間<br />\n同埋訓緊果陣冇晒意識咁<br />\n好似死左咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係到宜家就好鐘意訓教<br />\n訓左就咩都唔使煩唔洗理<br />\n覺得平時我地訓教<br />\n根本就係練習緊以後既死亡<br />\n好似就唔太怕死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f373f40686d33d4bb1e934e8a3e0a74f1d44d3e2","tid":785583,"uid":103315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:33:34.000Z","msg":"為黎為去咪又係死 但求在世開心有成功感only"},{"pid":"693250c7fe73070ac83bccd5faed57b59e7d3e16","tid":785583,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"睇下咩墳場<br />\n<br />\n香港墳場，赤柱墳場都好有美感"},{"pid":"7d540749bd9bdd650871534d546946e051c40bcf","tid":785583,"uid":182701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f373f40686d33d4bb1e934e8a3e0a74f1d44d3e2","tid":785583,"uid":103315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:33:34.000Z","msg":"為黎為去咪又係死 但求在世開心有成功感only"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"就係唔知幾時會開心 幾時先唔使捱<br />\n辛苦幾十年到頭黎唔知為乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127b4a3dc42e159d47ba0e8153da372593f7ac0e","tid":785583,"uid":162409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d540749bd9bdd650871534d546946e051c40bcf","tid":785583,"uid":182701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f373f40686d33d4bb1e934e8a3e0a74f1d44d3e2","tid":785583,"uid":103315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:33:3